pr_title: Initial setup: gradle, lint, styles, preview app
pr_body:
- theme, typography tokens, size and padding values that the apps will use
- lint rules: 
    - rule to prohibit using some attributes like textColor, textSize, background tint etc.
    - rule to only allow `Mifos.DesignSystem.Spacing.*` values for margin and paddings
    - rule to only allow `wrap_content`, `match_parent`, `0dp` and `Mifos.DesignSystem.Size` values for height and width
    - rule to detect if styles other than the ui library are used 
- some utility functions to do things like getting a color from theme attributes(`context.getThemeAttributeColor(R.attr.colorPrimary)`), specifying dp values directly(`2.dp`)
- profile image view
- publication on jitpack
Preference Fragment dialogs' use platform dialog builder, so styles don't get apply correctly. So this is fix for that.

pr_body:
### Styling and ui library integration for these screens:
- bottom navigation screen: search screen, client list, group list, center list
- drawer screens: checker inbox, individual collection sheet, collection sheet, run report, path tracker, settings, about


### Changes
- dark theme issues taken care of
- status bar color contrast for both dark and light theme
- Spinners converted to AutoCompleteTextView(text field with options) or dialogs with radio button list
- Showing visually the selection of list items in client, group and center list
- date picker fields and dialogs


### Things
- Date picker on new individual screen doesn't look right in dark mode in the recording but last commit fixes that
- Settings screen dialogs will look like other dialogs after [mifso-ui-library/pull/4](https://github.com/openMF/mifos-ui-library/pull/4) is added 
- Due to how app is structured
   - snackbars doesn't show correctly and shows over the bottom navigation 
   - app bar elevation doesn't behave correctly with scrollable screen
- this PR also contains commits from #1887 which is not merged yet.

- [ ] Github actions CI Java version to 11 for the newer version of Android gradle plugin needs to be updated to pass the workflows
- updated plugins and some dependencies' versions
- updated targetSdk
- replaced findbugs with spotbugs as findbugs is deprecated and can't be used in gradle 6 and later versions

- touch intercept for recycler view item click listener was not working after updates so replaced with onclick lambda passed as  parameter to recycler view adapter

pr_title: UI library integration and dependencies update
pr_body:
- updated kotlin and gradle versions
- updated Github actions CI Java version to 11 for the newer version of Android gradle plugin
- updated plugins and some dependencies' versions
- updated targetSdk to 31
- replaced findbugs with spotbugs as findbugs is deprecated and can't be used in gradle 6 and later versions

Commit [d3a4d7f](https://github.com/openMF/mifos-mobile/pull/1864/commits/d3a4d7f1d4546c2ab7a519dcd495314f540ceb4e):
- updated ui dependencies
- touch intercept for recycler view item click listener was not working so replaced with on click lambda passed as  parameter
- appCompat to material

Other commits: ui improvements and adding ui library
